Cam::

She slowly stood up, trying not to wake the baby. She cradled the 
baby in her arms and walked slowly to the entrance. She was Windlord 
and smiled. "Hey, were in the galaxy have you been. I've been a big 
bot here and took care of this helpless baby. She was all alone when 
I found here. Were is her mommy and daddy? They didn't go to the same 
place were my mommy and daddy are did they? If hey did, then I should 
take care of the baby. I'm a big bot now. So I can do stuff like 
that."

Battera:;
She looked down at the small child carrying the baby. She sighed and 
remembered her younger days. "You must be a very big bot in order to 
take care of  child like that. I am impressed. You seem to be doing a 
very good job there."

Cam:  
She smiled at Battera's words and puffed up her small chest a bit. "I 
am a big bot huh?"
